================================================================================
ABOUT PRUNING
================================================================================
Model pruning removes low-magnitude weights to reduce model size.
This benchmark tests L1 unstructured pruning at different sparsity levels.

Pruning amounts to test: ['10%', '20%', '30%', '40%', '50%']

