================================================================================
RECOMMENDATIONS:
================================================================================
• 10-20% pruning: Minimal quality loss, good for production
• 30% pruning: Balanced size/quality trade-off
• 40-50% pruning: Aggressive, may degrade quality significantly

NOTE: Always validate output quality on your specific use case!
Pruning affects different model architectures differently.

